01:08:34.151 --> 01:08:36.861
They ought to call them "the Sams,"
don't you think?

01:08:37.738 --> 01:08:39.697
You're tired, huh?

01:08:40.116 --> 01:08:42.658
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

