McCLINTOCK: The most optimistic projection
USAMRIID is willing to make...

01:08:48.832 --> 01:08:52.001
...for the spread of the virus is this:
24 hours...

01:08:52.169 --> 01:08:54.170
...36 hours...

01:08:54.337 --> 01:08:56.256
...48 hours.

01:08:56.423 --> 01:08:59.216
