must be viewed objectively.

01:08:59.385 --> 01:09:03.720
Be compassionate,
but be compassionate globally.

01:09:04.180 --> 01:09:05.348
Thank you.

01:09:06.642 --> 01:09:08.475
All right, all right. Please. Please.

01:09:08.644 --> 01:09:12.104
