a certain number of losses.

01:19:28.346 --> 01:19:29.847
Robby's infected.

01:19:32.851 --> 01:19:33.851
I'm sorry.

01:19:34.686 --> 01:19:36.437
Is "we" sorry too?

01:19:40.108 --> 01:19:44.445
