that within 48 hours...

01:21:13.910 --> 01:21:17.997
...this virus could be crawling across
the White House lawn, he gave the order.

01:21:18.164 --> 01:21:19.707
I wasn't invited.

01:21:21.042 --> 01:21:23.794
